{"name":"UnicodeBasic","instances":[],"imports":["Init","UnicodeBasic.Types","UnicodeBasic.UnicodeData","UnicodeBasic.PropList"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L897-L897","name":"Unicode.isAlpha","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isAlpha","doc":"Check if alphabetic character\n\nUnicode property: `Alphabetic` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L888-L894","name":"Unicode.isAlphabetic","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isAlphabetic","doc":"Check if alphabetic character\n\nUnicode property: `Alphabetic` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L881-L882","name":"Unicode.isMath","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isMath","doc":"Check if mathematical symbol character\n\nUnicode property: `Math` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L849-L875","name":"Unicode.isCaseIgnorable","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isCaseIgnorable","doc":"Check if character is ignorable for casing purposes\n\nGenerated from general categories `Lm`, `Mn`, `Me`, `Sk`, `Cf`, and word\nbreak properties `MidLetter`, `MidNumLet`, `Single_Quote`.\n\nUnicode property: `Case_Ignorable` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L834-L840","name":"Unicode.isCased","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isCased","doc":"Check if cased letter character\n\nUnicode properties: `Cased` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L827-L828","name":"Unicode.isUppercase","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isUppercase","doc":"Check if uppercase letter character\n\nUnicode property: `Uppercase` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L820-L821","name":"Unicode.isLowercase","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isLowercase","doc":"Check if lowercase letter character\n\nUnicode property: `Lowercase` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L809-L814","name":"Unicode.isWhiteSpace","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isWhiteSpace","doc":"Check if white space character\n\nUnicode property: `White_Space`\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L778-L798","name":"Unicode.getHexDigit?","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getHexDigit?","doc":"Get value of digit\n\nUnicode properties: `Hex_Digit` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L765-L772","name":"Unicode.isHexDigit","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isHexDigit","doc":"Check if character represents a digit in base 16\n\nUnicode property: `Hex_Digit` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L754-L759","name":"Unicode.getDecimalRange?","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getDecimalRange?","doc":"Get decimal digit range\n\nIf the character is part of a contiguous sequence representing the ten\ndecimal digits in order from 0 to 9, this function returns the first and\nlast characters from this range.\n\nUnicode property: `Numeric_Type=Decimal` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L741-L744","name":"Unicode.isDecimal","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isDecimal","doc":"Check if character represents a decimal digit\n\nFor this property, a character must be part of a contiguous sequence\nrepresenting the ten decimal digits in order from 0 to 9.\n\nUnicode property: `Numeric_Type=Decimal` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L717-L732","name":"Unicode.getDigit?","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getDigit?","doc":"Get value of digit\n\nUnicode properties: `Numeric_Value`, `Numeric_Type=Digit` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L703-L711","name":"Unicode.isDigit","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isDigit","doc":"Check if character represents a digit in base 10\n\nUnicode property: `Numeric_Type=Digit` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L688-L697","name":"Unicode.isNumeric.otherNumeric","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isNumeric.otherNumeric","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L678-L697","name":"Unicode.isNumeric","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isNumeric","doc":"Check if character represents a numerical value\n\nUnicode property: `Numeric_Type=Numeric` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L658-L667","name":"Unicode.getCanonicalDecomposition.loop","kind":"opaque","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getCanonicalDecomposition.loop","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L646-L668","name":"Unicode.getCanonicalDecomposition","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getCanonicalDecomposition","doc":"Get canonical decomposition of character (`NFD`)\n\nUnicode property: `Decomposition_Mapping` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L634-L637","name":"Unicode.getTitleChar","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getTitleChar","doc":"Map character to titlecase\n\nThis function does not handle the case where the titlecase mapping would\nconsist of more than one character.\n\nUnicode property: `Simple_Titlecase_Mapping` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L622-L625","name":"Unicode.getUpperChar","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getUpperChar","doc":"Map character to uppercase\n\nThis function does not handle the case where the uppercase mapping would\nconsist of more than one character.\n\nUnicode property: `Simple_Uppercase_Mapping` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L610-L613","name":"Unicode.getLowerChar","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getLowerChar","doc":"Map character to lowercase\n\nThis function does not handle the case where the lowercase mapping would\nconsist of more than one character.\n\nUnicode property: `Simple_Lowercase_Mapping` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L595-L595","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isCn","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isCn","doc":"Check if unassigned character (`Cn`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Cn` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L589-L592","name