","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isPunctuation","doc":"Check if punctuation character (`P`)\n\nThis is a derived category (`P = Pc | Pd | Ps | Pe | Pi | Pf | Po`).\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=P` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L312-L312","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isNo","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isNo","doc":"Check if other number character (`No`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=No` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L306-L309","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isOtherNumber","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isOtherNumber","doc":"Check if other number character (`No`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=No` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L300-L300","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isNl","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isNl","doc":"Check if letter number character (`Nl`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Nl` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L294-L297","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLetterNumber","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLetterNumber","doc":"Check if letter number character (`Nl`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Nl` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L288-L288","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isNd","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isNd","doc":"Check if decimal number character (`Nd`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Nd` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L282-L285","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isDecimalNumber","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isDecimalNumber","doc":"Check if decimal number character (`Nd`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Nd` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L276-L276","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isN","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isN","doc":"Check if number character (`N`)\n\nThis is a derived category (`N = Nd | Nl | No`).\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=N` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L270-L273","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isNumber","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isNumber","doc":"Check if number character (`N`)\n\nThis is a derived category (`N = Nd | Nl | No`).\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=N` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L262-L262","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isMe","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isMe","doc":"Check if enclosing combining mark character (`Me`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Me` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L256-L259","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isEnclosingMark","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isEnclosingMark","doc":"Check if enclosing combining mark character (`Me`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Me` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L250-L250","na