 derived category (`M = Mn | Mc | Me`).\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=M` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L212-L212","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLo","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLo","doc":"Check if other letter character (`Lo`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Lo`"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L206-L209","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isOtherLetter","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isOtherLetter","doc":"Check if other letter character (`Lo`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Lo`"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L200-L200","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLm","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLm","doc":"Check if modifier letter character (`Lm`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Lm`"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L194-L197","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isModifierLetter","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isModifierLetter","doc":"Check if modifier letter character (`Lm`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Lm`"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L188-L188","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLC","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLC","doc":"Check if cased letter character (`LC`)\n\nThis is a derived category (`L = Lu | Ll | Lt`).\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=LC` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L180-L185","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isCasedLetter","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isCasedLetter","doc":"Check if cased letter character (`LC`)\n\nThis is a derived category (`L = Lu | Ll | Lt`).\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=LC` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L172-L172","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLu","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLu","doc":"Check if uppercase letter character (`Lu`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Lu` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L166-L169","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isUppercaseLetter","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isUppercaseLetter","doc":"Check if uppercase letter character (`Lu`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Lu` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L160-L160","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLt","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLt","doc":"Check if titlecase letter character (`Lt`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Lt` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L154-L157","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isTitlecaseLetter","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isTitlecaseLetter","doc":"Check if titlecase letter character (`Lt`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Lt` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L148-L148","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLl","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLl","doc":"Check if lowercase letter character (`Ll`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Ll` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L142-L145","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLowercaseLetter","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLowercaseLetter","doc":"Check if lowercase letter character (`Ll`)\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=Ll` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L136-L136","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isL","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isL","doc":"Check if letter character (`L`)\n\nThis is a derived category (`L = Lu | Ll | Lt | Lm | Lo`).\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=L` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L130-L133","name":"Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLetter","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.GeneralCategory.isLetter","doc":"Check if letter character (`L`)\n\nThis is a derived category (`L = Lu | Ll | Lt | Lm | Lo`).\n\nUnicode Property: `General_Category=L` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L113-L120","name":"Unicode.isInGeneralCategory","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isInGeneralCategory","doc":"Check if character belongs to the general category\n\nUnicode property: `General_Category` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L106-L107","name":"Unicode.getGeneralCategory","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getGeneralCategory","doc":"Get character general category\n\n*Caveat*: This function never returns a derived general category. Use\n`Unicode.isInGeneralCategory` to check whether a character belongs to a\ngeneral category (derived or not).\n\nUnicode property: `General_Category` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L87-L92","name":"Unicode.isBidiControl","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isBidiControl","doc":"Check if bidirectional control character\n\nUnicode property: `Bidi_Control` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L80-L81","name":"Unicode.isBidiMirrored","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isBidiMirrored","doc":"Check if bidirectional mirrored character\n\nUnicode property: `Bidi_Mirrored` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L73-L74","name":"Unicode.getBidiClass","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getBidiClass","doc":"Get character bidirectional class\n\nUnicode property: `Bidi_Class` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/76009f336f6dfc3086024cee9d7a5d0c1f800258/UnicodeBasic.lean#L62-L63","name":"Unicode.getName","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.getName","doc":"Get character name\n\nWhen the Unicode property `Name` is empty, a unique code label is returned\nas described in Unicode Standard, section 4.8. These labels start with\n`'<'` (U+003C) and end with `'>'` (U+003E) so they are distinguishable from\nactual name values.\n\nUnicode property: `Name`\n"}]}